<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA97">
<l>eṅkaḷ perumā ṉimaiyōr talaimakaṉī</l>
<l>ceṅka ṇeṭumā ṟirumārpā – poṅku</l>
<l>paṭamūkki ṉāyiravāyp pāmpaṇaimēṟ cērntāy</l>
<l>kuṭamūkkiṟ kōyilāk koṇṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You [are] our great lord, the leader of the Unblinking ones,</l>
<l>red-eyed tall Māl, you with Śrī on [your] chest, you joined</l>
<l>the bed [that is] a snake with a thousand mouths [and] noses, with rising hoods,</l>
<l>taking Kuṭamūkku as a temple.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
